data.description: This is a beautiful home built in 2006. Lots of green grass to enjoy. Open floor plan with maintenance free sealed fireplace. Large 3 car garage. Lots of concrete flatwork in the back & side yard for easy maintenance. One of the bedrooms is currently used as an office. Walk in Closet in the Master Bedroom. Separate Tub & Shower in the Master. The hall bathroom has doors that open to both hallways. Indoor Laundry in a separate room Large covered patio outside the slider next to the dining room/kitchen. Access to the back yard from the Master Suite as well. Brokered And Advertised By: Volsch Enterprises, Inc. Listing Agent: Charlotte J. Volsch
